data.meta_description:
Actress Dina Merrill and actor Cliff Robertson leave Washington DC, the state of her mother, serial heiress Marjorie Merriweather Post (left), after their wedding, 21st, December. It was the second marriage for both. The Robertsons have appeared in several films together.
22 December 1966
